short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: YouTube Enhancer is a simple extension that adds some useful features to YouTube.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
🚀 Enhance your YouTube experience with this powerful browser extension. Features include customizable volume control, automatic quality settings, playback speed adjustments, volume boost, and more. Build from scratch with easy steps.

Transform your YouTube experience with the YouTube Enhancer Extension. Build it yourself or contribute on GitHub. Open-source under MIT License. Elevate your viewing experience! 🌟

🔣 Supported languages:
English (US) (100%), Русский (100%), 中文 (简体) (100%), Italiano (98%), 日本語 (98%), Svenska (SV) (98%), 繁體中文 (台灣) (94%), Türkçe (75%), Português do Brasil (74%), Français (67%), Español (63%), Deutsch (36%), Català (0%), Čeština (0%), فارسی (0%), עברית (0%), Hindi (0%), Polish (0%)
Help us translating the extension to your language - https://crowdin.com/project/youtube-enhancer

If you love what I do and want to support me, consider buying me a coffee on Ko-fi ☕. Your contribution helps me continue enhancing your YouTube journey!
